Introduction

Tia is an American singer and model. She was the main dancer, vocalist and rapper of the disbanded group ChoColat.

Before debuting as a singer she worked as an MC for a children's TV show.

She debuted as a solo singer in May 25h, 2018 with her digital single "No More".
